y benefit as well as yours &#8212; of what I posted last year, about <a href=\"http://ihnatko.com/2011/04/18/fast-eddie-lets-play-some-pool/\" target=\"_blank\">the inspirational possibilities of &#8220;The Hustler&#8221;</a>.</p>
